<%- include('./partials/header') %>
<!-- user login -->
<div
  id="loginDiv"
  class="col-8 p-2 rounded border border-light needs-validation"
>
  <div class="mb-3">
    <input
      type="email"
      id="email_login"
      value="gigi@gmail.com"
      pattern="[a-z0-9._%+-]+@[a-z0-9.-]+\.[a-z]{2,}$"
      class="form-control"
      required
    />
  </div>
  <div class="mb-3">
    <input
      type="password"
      id="password_login"
      value="123"
      pattern="[a-z0-9._%+-]+@[a-z0-9.-]+\.[a-z]{2,}$"
      class="form-control"
      required
    />
  </div>
  <div class="mb-3 d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
    <button id="loginBtn" class="btn btn-primary form-control">LOG IN</button>
  </div>
  <button id="signupBtn" class="btn btn-info form-control">SIGN UP</button>
</div>

<!-- user sign up  -->
<div
  id="signupDiv"
  style="display: none"
  class="col-8 p-2 rounded border border-light needs-validation"
>
  <div class="mb-3">
    <input
      type="text"
      name="display_name"
      id="display_name"
      placeholder="Display Name*"
      class="form-control"
      required
    />
  </div>
  <div class="mb-3">
    <input
      type="email"
      name="email"
      id="email_signup"
      placeholder="Email*"
      class="form-control"
      pattern="[a-z0-9._%+-]+@[a-z0-9.-]+\.[a-z]{2,}$"
    />
  </div>
  <div class="mb-3">
    <input
      type="password"
      name="password"
      id="password_signup"
      placeholder="Password*"
      class="form-control"
      required
    />
  </div>
  <div class="mb-3 d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
    <button id="submitBtn" class="btn btn-info form-control">Submit</button>
  </div>
</div>
<div id="gameRules">
  <h5 class="text-center">How to play?</h5>
  <p>
    Werewolf is a super fun game that can be played with a group of people. The
    object of the game is to identify and kill the werewolves amongst the
    villagers.
  </p>
  <ol>
    <li>1. Assemble at least 6 players to join the same game room.</li>
    <li>
      2. Each player will be assigned a role eight werewolf or villager
      automatically once join the room.
    </li>
    <li>
      3. Game starts from Night mode: werewolf will vote to kill a villager,
      highest vote gets killed, then game switch to Day mode.
    </li>
    <li>
      4. During Day mode, all alive players can vote to kill a "werewolf", then
      game switch to Night mode again if there is no winner.
    </li>
    <li>
      5. If all werewolves are killed, then villager wins, or the contrary.
    </li>
  </ol>
</div>
<a id="gameHallBtn" style="display: none" href="/gameHall" class="btn btn-info"
  >Enter GameHall</a
>
<%- include('./partials/footer') %>
